/>\n<br />\n身為基督徒的他引用聖經經文「如今常存的有信，有望，有愛這三樣，其中最大的是愛。」他表明從不憎恨令他受傷的警察暴徒，因為仇恨只會蒙蔽理智，只有愛和包容，才能解決彼此矛盾。而多元社會應可容納不同聲音，除了黑警之外，因為黑警會死全家的。如果大家都向同一方向前行，社會抗爭將會很快成功。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T03:58:48.000Z","msg":"小心耶佬是鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92adec2b3e05f17e7b7ccb433add40474bf467f4","tid":2056830,"uid":244818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T04:00:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"393c6537d8b3112cec7a78a219d11e54d3bd1a06","tid":2056830,"uid":46447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T04:02:33.000Z","msg":"笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fbfb355c476646c9fc476dd2d4bd5f6c8731640","tid":2056830,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T04:03:01.000Z","msg":"屌你笑撚死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5d31b48ee9c3750d8b359557cf94a859342d485","tid":2056830,"uid":177047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b6228c8b4cae97dfc47df497a2aa03d61094e305","tid":2056830,"uid":216326,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T03:34:54.000Z","msg":"右面支旗改埋做齊上齊落就完美"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T04:03:15.000Z","msg":"下款改埋：志同道合撐手足群組敬上"},{"pid":"7b738ee840231e06b7bc26f50776884b4438b2eb","tid":2056830,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T04:04:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><